<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üìß Email Reader (IMAP)</h1>

        <div class="info">
            <h3>Setup Instructions:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Generate an App Password for your Gmail account:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Go to your Google Account settings</li>
                        <li>Security ‚Üí 2-Step Verification ‚Üí App passwords</li>
                        <li>Generate a new app password for "Mail"</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Copy <span class="code">.env.example</span> to <span class="code">.env</span></li>
                <li>Add your email and app password to the <span class="code">.env</span> file</li>
                <li>Run <span class="code">npm install</span> and <span class="code">npm start</span></li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
