            proceeding.
        </div>

        <p>Test your email connection first, then view your emails:</p>

        <a href="/test-connection" class="btn btn-test" target="_blank">üîß Test Connection</a>
        <a href="/emails" class="btn">üìß View Emails</a>

        <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
